{"tid":2224075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府終於肯搞選舉啦！11月21號星期六！","createTime":"2020-09-30T09:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T14:39:43.000Z","uid":210495,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52a79979158563f7e7c4a15a848aaf514bf2c7d0","tid":2224075,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"無錯！政府終於肯搞<span class=\"small\">勞顧會僱員代表</span>選舉啦！<br />\n<br />\n仆街肯搞勞顧會選舉但係唔肯搞立法會選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還我立法會選舉！LegCo Election now!<br />\n<br />\n 勞工處邀請已根據《職工會條例》登記的僱員工會，登記為二○二一至二○二二年度勞工顧問委員會（勞顧會）僱員代表選舉的選舉單位、委任獲授權代表在選舉中投票，及提名候選人參選。<br />\n<br />\n  勞工處發言人今日（九月二十八日）表示：「我們今日開始接受選舉單位登記、委任獲授權代表及候選人提名，截止日期為二○二○年十月二十日（星期二）。」<br />\n<br />\n  現屆勞顧會委員的任期將於今年十二月三十一日屆滿。<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">新一屆僱員委員的選舉將於今年十一月二十一日（星期六）在美孚政府綜合大樓一樓美孚社區會堂舉行，獲授權代表可在當日上午九時至下午五時期間於上述投票站投票</span></span></strong>，以選出五名僱員代表出任下屆勞顧會委員，任期兩年至二○二二年十二月三十一日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202009/28/P2020092500685.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202009%2F28%2FP2020092500685.htm&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyvsf6ZhrNwlVLGl95Ukzwcs%3D&h=ee2b130a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202009/28/P2020092500685.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5201eb11adbea0afb99621c846e497df1c1b648b","tid":2224075,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"01ab190cc83a4878b61648fff522065a83787116","tid":2224075,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10cfcd9a3158ddb9c0103a9b272c6806e6ac639e","tid":2224075,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"p